2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper mentions the use of deep learning algorithms. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper proposes enhancements to the state of the art in this domain. 
4. cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible category as the paper deals with image reconstruction. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is another possible category as the paper proposes a dataset composed of pictures from the Metropolitan Museum of Art.
